                <note rend="inline" type="source">838.105/466: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Haiti</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Drew</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-09-29T13:00:00-05:00"
                            >September 29, 1933—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>71. Your despatch No. 131, September 20, 1933. You are authorized to sign the
                    amendment to the Garde Agreement as submitted in the above-mentioned
                    despatch.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
